The header,cpp and main files are included here, all you need to do is 

Instalation
1)install opencv
2)create a system path for it
3)put all the installed files in the same folder
4)run the main file (h.cpp)(it should generate a .exe which you can use whenever)


Using the program
1)put your hand over the two purple squares and press the "S" key to take a skin sample
2)press "B" after moving your hand out of the camera frame
3)enjoy
